Dia. 02 Endgame
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is hard to think during an actual game that it is possible to capture Black.
\par
\par There is big chance that White is going to block at 1 for \cf1\b endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Then Black is satisfied living with 2.
\par
\par If Black tries to live with many points and plays at A instead of 2, White plays at 2 and Black is in big trouble.
\par }
