Dia. 03 Another Solution?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's attachment at 1 is a sharp idea.
\par The \cf1\b 2-2 point \cf0\b0 is also a vital point in the corner.
\par
\par If Black plays hane at 2, White 3 is a suitable move and White can capture Black up to 7.
\par
\par Is it another solution then?
\par No~
\par }
