Dia. 04 Live with Miai
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against White \'a1\'e2, Black's attachment at 1 is the vital point for living.
\par
\par If White plays at A, Black lives with B. Moreover if White plays at B, Black lives with A.
\par In other words, A and B are \cf1\b miai\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
\par }
